# Notes
###############################################################################

# Configuration:
# - Core Pool Size: 5
# - Max Pool Size: 10
# - Queue Capacity: 25
#
# Metrics to watch:
# - activeCount: Threads currently executing
# - poolSize: Current thread count
# - queueSize: Tasks waiting
# - utilizationPercent: Thread usage %
# - queueUtilizationPercent: Queue usage %
